'''TDF104''' was the class name of the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] ship owned by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Oxus]]. [[Han Solo's pirate ship|Oxus's ship]] was stolen by [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] and [[Montross (bounty hunter)|Montross Holdaack]], members of its crew, to take [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Starkiller]] and his [[Droid/Legends|droids]] to [[Ogana Major]].

==Characteristics==
A TDF104 was an elongated, complex-looking ship. A lounge area in the center of the vessel served also as the main entrance, and a ramp extended from it to the surface to allow crew and passengers to board. The cockpit of a TDF104 accommodated two [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]]. Between the lounge and the cockpit was a long corridor with a control panel which transmitted electronic signals to and from the pilots' stations to the fuselage.

TDF104s were equipped with powerful scanning systems and [[Escape pod/Legends|life pods]]. Two turrets held [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]].

